A serene Buddhist monk in saffron robes sits in meditation posture beneath an ancient Bodhi tree, surrounded by swirling golden sound waves that emanate outward like ripples on water. The scene is bathed in warm amber light filtering through heart-shaped Bodhi leaves. Delicate lotus flowers float in a still pond nearby, their petals catching the ethereal vibrations. The atmosphere is peaceful and transcendent, with soft mist rising from the ground. Studio Ghibli style with gentle watercolor textures, dreamy color palette of deep greens, warm golds, and soft purples, featuring flowing organic lines and a sense of magical tranquility.
